# Local-only internal security docs — open vulnerabilities, missing hardening,
# attack surface, incident history. Never publish; only defensible measures go
# in the published docs (apps/docs-ophis). Keep on operator's machine only.
docs/security/*.local.md

# Private affiliate program data — Super VIP roster, per-deal negotiated rates,
# live invite codes. Invite-only and confidential; never public. Operator only.
docs/affiliate/

